icationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">People</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5937183\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<p>People have been part of Grand Canyon's history and culture from 10,000 years ago through today. Eleven contemporary tribes have cultural links to the area, and their oral histories are rich with references to the creation of that great chasm and torrential river. From the sixteenth century on, tribes familiar with the region were guides and informants for Spanish and later Euro-American explorers. The quiet area of the South Rim rapidly expanded into the Grand Canyon Village when entrepreneurs and miners came hoping to make a fortune. Passing through or calling the canyon home, many people have influenced the development and protection of Grand Canyon for themselves, for visitors, and for the National Park Service.</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6278631\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6278631\">\n<div class=\"Component FeatureGrid\">\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -large\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/historyculture/associated-tribes.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/learn/historyculture/associated-tribes.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"Prehistoric granaries along the Colorado River.\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 1300px, (min-width: 1200px) 1120px, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/1BFCA9F5-9F5D-DA19-BE0A75DEBB135E9C.jpg?width=1300&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/1BFCA9F5-9F5D-DA19-BE0A75DEBB135E9C.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/1BFCA9F5-9F5D-DA19-BE0A75DEBB135E9C.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/1BFCA9F5-9F5D-DA19-BE0A75DEBB135E9C.jpg?width=1300&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 1300w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">Associated Tribes</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Eleven contemporary tribes have cultural links to the area and call Grand Canyon home.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -medium\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/historyculture/explorers.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/learn/historyculture/explorers.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A black and white photo of John Wesley Powell\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 640px, (min-width: 1200px) 550px, (min-width: 576px) 50vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/186FA5B6-B6A9-8FB9-4C46DC15D55FE837.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/186FA5B6-B6A9-8FB9-4C46DC15D55FE837.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/186FA5B6-B6A9-8FB9-4C46DC15D55FE837.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">Early Explorers</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Native Americans guided the earliest European and American explorers seeking riches and adventure into canyon country.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -medium\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/historyculture/miners.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/learn/historyculture/miners.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A black and white photo of a hotel on the rim of the canyon.\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 640px, (min-width: 1200px) 550px, (min-width: 576px) 50vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/268E4B3F-BE61-D00F-0B111960D85CAFBB.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/268E4B3F-BE61-D00F-0B111960D85CAFBB.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/268E4B3F-BE61-D00F-0B111960D85CAFBB.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">Miners</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Miners came to Grand Canyon to exploit its resources, but many found the tourist industry more profitable and started offering guided tours.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -medium\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/articles/000/native-art-and-activism-of-the-grand-canyon.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/articles/000/native-art-and-activism-of-the-grand-canyon.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"Nampeyo working on pottery inside\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 640px, (min-width: 1200px) 550px, (min-width: 576px) 50vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/8EA1B0AD-A0F7-607A-B5F14C8C903CF319.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/8EA1B0AD-A0F7-607A-B5F14C8C903CF319.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/8EA1B0AD-A0F7-607A-B5F14C8C903CF319.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">Native Art and Activism</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Native American individuals from Grand Canyon's affiliated tribes have long used art for cultural practice and as a part of activism. </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -medium\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/articles/000/-little-mexico-and-creating-community.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/articles/000/-little-mexico-and-creating-community.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"Bright Angel Lodge between 1920s and 1930s\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 640px, (min-width: 1200px) 550px, (min-width: 576px) 50vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/8E844034-D96A-6D64-EF1A2F230D4339DB.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/8E844034-D96A-6D64-EF1A2F230D4339DB.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/8E844034-D96A-6D64-EF1A2F230D4339DB.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">The \"Little Mexico\" Community</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">The \"Little Mexico\" community formed on the South Rim from 1919-1929 and is a story of resilience and resourcefulness. </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -medium\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/historyculture/entrepeneurs.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/learn/historyculture/entrepeneurs.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"John Verkamp in front of his tent.\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 640px, (min-width: 1200px) 550px, (min-width: 576px) 50vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/214B190F-0E07-4A2C-2BD4BE784547DC36.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/214B190F-0E07-4A2C-2BD4BE784547DC36.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/214B190F-0E07-4A2C-2BD4BE784547DC36.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">Entrepreneurs</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">After the Santa Fe Railroad started bringing visitors to the canyon, entrepreneurs came to the canyon to make their fortune.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -medium\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/historyculture/ccc.htm?cs_forceReadMode=1\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/learn/historyculture/ccc.htm?cs_forceReadMode=1', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A black and white photo of two men installing a telephone pole.\" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 640px, (min-width: 1200px) 550px, (min-width: 576px) 50vw, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/1F5D3855-A55C-303C-1FA60DCD20A5DC0E.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/1F5D3855-A55C-303C-1FA60DCD20A5DC0E.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/1F5D3855-A55C-303C-1FA60DCD20A5DC0E.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">Civilian Conservation Corps</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Company 819 arrived on May 29, 1933 and continued on the South Rim until the end of the program in July, 1942.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"FeatureGrid-item\">\n<div class=\"Component Feature -large\">\n<a class=\"Feature-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/historyculture/whose-story-is-history.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send', 'event', 'Feature Grid - Prioritized', document.location.href, '/grca/learn/historyculture/whose-story-is-history.htm', 1, true)\">\n<div class=\"Feature-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"Images of Nampeyo, CCC members, Pauline Patraw Mead, and George Murakami. \" class=\"Feature-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1380px) 1300px, (min-width: 1200px) 1120px, 100vw\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/922CA915-F052-14D2-647FC15B0DCD528A.jpg?width=1300&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/922CA915-F052-14D2-647FC15B0DCD528A.jpg?width=420&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 420w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/922CA915-F052-14D2-647FC15B0DCD528A.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 640w, /common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop16_9/922CA915-F052-14D2-647FC15B0DCD528A.jpg?width=1300&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop 1300w\"/>\n<div class=\"Feature-title carrot-end\">Whose Story Is History?</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"Feature-description\">Bringing the Diverse History of Grand Canyon into the Light</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5964127\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5964127\"><div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup CaptionedImage\">\n<figure class=\"-auto-width\">\n<a href=\"http://grcahistory.org/\">\n<img alt=\"Banner image linking to ASU Nature, Culture and History at the Grand Canyon shows Grand Canyon mules on a trail with superimposed letters: ASU Nature, Culture and History at the Grand Canyon\" src=\"/grca/learn/historyculture/images/asu-banner960-jpg.JPG?maxwidth=1300&amp;maxheight=1300&amp;autorotate=false&amp;format=webp\" title=\"Banner image linking to ASU Nature, Culture and History at the Grand Canyon shows Grand Canyon mules on a trail with superimposed letters: ASU Nature, Culture and History at the Grand Canyon\"/>\n</a>\n<figcaption>The \"Nature, Culture and History at Grand Canyon\" website is Grand Canyon National Park's  primary online source of historical and cultural information, Click on the photo above to visit site. </figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6195422\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6195422\">\n\n<div class=\"ListingList ListingResults container\" id=\"searchListing-8439DF95-A0B1-E0FB-3F2F5811FFA412C5\">\n<h2 class=\"margin-bottom-1\">Grand Canyon Historical Stories</h2>\n<div class=\"grid-row grid-gap\">\n<div class=\"grid-col-12\">\n<div class=\"results\">\n<a name=\"results\"></a>\n<div class=\"display-list-view\" id=\"display-list-view\">\n<div class=\"info-micro-filter\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<!-- result count -->\n<div class=\"result-count usa-hint\"></div>\n<!-- controls (kept original hooks, added USWDS classes) -->\n<div class=\"result-selectors display-flex flex-wrap gap-2\">\n<!-- Parks facet -->\n<div class=\"result-facet-Parks_Item result-facet-select\" data-facetfield=\"Parks_Item\" data-facettitle=\"Location\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<form action=\"#\" class=\"micro-filter facet-parks usa-form\">\n<label class=\"usa-label usa-sr-only\" for=\"result-narrow-Parks_Item-searchListing-8439DF95-A0B1-E0FB-3F2F5811FFA412C5\">Narrow By Location</label>\n<select class=\"usa-select\" id=\"result-narrow-Parks_Item-searchListing-8439DF95-A0B1-E0FB-3F2F5811FFA412C5\" multiple=\"\" name=\"result-narrow-Parks_Item\"></select>\n</form>\n</div>\n<!-- Organizations facet -->\n<div class=\"result-facet-Organizations_Item result-facet-select\" data-facetfield=\"Organizations_Item\" data-facettitle=\"Office\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<form action=\"#\" class=\"micro-filter facet-organizations usa-form\">\n<label class=\"usa-label usa-sr-only\" for=\"result-narrow-Organizations_Item-searchListing-8439DF95-A0B1-E0FB-3F2F5811FFA412C5\">Narrow By Office</label>\n<select class=\"usa-select\" id=\"result-narrow-Organizations_Item-searchListing-8439DF95-A0B1-E0FB-3F2F5811FFA412C5\" multiple=\"\" name=\"result-narrow-Organizations_Item\"></select>\n</form>\n</di